      <title>司法部采取行动接管特朗普对1月6日诉讼的辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/doj-moves-to-take-over-trump-defense-against-jan-6-lawsuits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部正在寻求代表唐纳德·特朗普总统在长期运行的民事诉讼中进行干预，指控他在2021年1月6日，在2021年1月6日袭击中对美国国会大厦的暴力和破坏承担责任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/doj-moves-to-take-over-trump-defense-against-jan-6-lawsuits</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 16:15:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰指控前部长透露秘密国防计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/poland-charges-former-minister-for-revealing-secret-defense-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰检察官指控前任民族主义政府的国防部长马里乌斯·布拉斯克扎克（Mariusz Blaszczak）在2023年议会大选之前披露了机密军事计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/poland-charges-former-minister-for-revealing-secret-defense-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 15:57:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国说，使用最强大的欧盟贸易工具在我们身上浮动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/france-said-to-float-using-eu-s-most-powerful-trade-tool-on-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国希望欧盟考虑在唐纳德·特朗普总统使用关税不公平地迫使集团进行政策变化的情况下，考虑对美国采取最强大的报复措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/france-said-to-float-using-eu-s-most-powerful-trade-tool-on-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 15:54:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的动手贷款，向其他机构提供的残疾计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/trump-hands-student-loans-disability-programs-to-other-agencies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统说，他正在急剧缩小的教育部门的关键职能将由小型企业管理局和卫生和公共服务部处理，因为担心他为改革联邦政府的努力可以减少一些计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/trump-hands-student-loans-disability-programs-to-other-agencies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 15:50:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏丹被世界战争肆虐世界已被忽视</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/sudan-civil-war-how-the-conflict-began-and-what-its-impact-has-been</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏丹军队与准军事团体之间的长期纠纷在2023年4月爆炸为成熟的内战。根据美国估计，从那以后，至少有15万人可能被杀，暴力事件的迹象几乎没有减轻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/sudan-civil-war-how-the-conflict-began-and-what-its-impact-has-been</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 15:33:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音击败了下一代美国战斗机合同的洛克希德</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/boeing-said-to-beat-lockheed-for-next-gen-fighter-jet-contract</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司赢得了一项合同，以设计和制造美国的下一代战斗机，击败了竞争对手洛克希德·马丁公司（Lockheed Martin Corp.）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/boeing-said-to-beat-lockheed-for-next-gen-fighter-jet-contract</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 15:15:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说加入英联邦国家“对我来说听起来不错”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/trump-says-us-joining-commonwealth-nations-sounds-good-to-me</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）似乎认可加入国民英联邦的想法；该组织主要由前英国殖民地组成，由查尔斯三世国王（King Charles III＆Mdash）经营；在社交媒体帖子中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/trump-says-us-joining-commonwealth-nations-sounds-good-to-me</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 15:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其骚动提示里拉自2023年以来的最糟糕的每周务虚会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/lira-set-for-worst-weekly-drop-since-2023-amid-turkey-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其里拉（Lira）在近两年内每周最陡峭的下降，随着紧急利率的增加未能阻止这种货币在越来越多的政治紧张局势中停止撤退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/lira-set-for-worst-weekly-drop-since-2023-amid-turkey-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 06:07:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管停火，但卢旺达支持的叛军扩大了刚果的土地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/rwanda-backed-rebels-expand-control-of-congo-despite-ceasefire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卢旺达支持的M23叛军在刚果民主共和国占领了第三个主要城镇，将其束缚扩大到该国矿产丰富的东部。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/rwanda-backed-rebels-expand-control-of-congo-despite-ceasefire</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 05:12:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国增加钴，铜的铜升至状态金属储量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/china-to-add-cobalt-copper-in-boost-to-state-metal-reserves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国计划在今年的关键工业金属中增加其战略储量，这是在能源过渡需求增加并且地缘政治紧张局势较高的时候提高关键矿物质供应的弹性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/china-to-add-cobalt-copper-in-boost-to-state-metal-reserves</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 00:31:01 GMT</pubDate>
